"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sniper_assassinate_dm2017_Description"							"Sniper locks onto a target enemy unit and, after %aim_duration%s, <font color='#70EA72'> fires a shot to the target and enemies within a radius of %radius% that deals critical damage and stuns them for %stun_duration%s.</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sniper_assassinate_dm2017_scepter_description"					"Increases the critical strike damage of Assassinate [Moon's Strike] by %crit_bonus%%%. Each point of attack speed reduces the cast point of this ability by %cast_point_reduce%%%, and it ignores the target's passive abilities."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sniper_assassinate_dm2017_Lore"									"In order to fulfill the prophecy and return to his home town, Kardel must make another shot as perfect as the one on the day of his ancient test."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sniper_assassinate_dm2017_Note0"									"Only allies can see the aimed effect."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sniper_assassinate_dm2017_Note1"									"The invisible cannot dodge the skill projectile."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_sniper_assassinate_dm2017_Note2"									"Channeling can be interrupted which ignores spell immune."
