//2022.11.22
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tusk_snowball_lua"							"SNOWBALL"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tusk_snowball_lua_Description"				"Tusk begins rolling into a snowball. Right-click an allied hero within %snowball_grab_radius% to add them to the snowball. Once launched, the snowball stuns and deals damage to all units in its path. The snowball's damage increases for each hero caught in it."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tusk_snowball_lua_Lore"						"Tales are still told of the wild feat that ended the grand brawl at White Fields."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tusk_snowball_lua_Note0"						"The snowball will break apart a maximum of 3 seconds after launch."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tusk_snowball_lua_Note1"						"The snowball can be launched early by pressing using the Launch Snowball ability."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tusk_snowball_lua_Note2"						"Doesn't carry illusions, but will carry Meepo clones and other units that Tusk controls."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tusk_snowball_lua_Note3"						"Meepo's clones can also be pulled into the snowball, increasing its damage and movement speed."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_tusk_snowball_lua_Note4"						"Allies can click on a snowball to add themselves to it."
