"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_lua_corrosive_Description"	"Armor is reduced by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_lua_red"			"Splash Attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form_lua_red_Description"	"Splashes attack damage to nearby units."
