"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_treant_large_tree_grab"									"Tree Grab"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_treant_large_tree_grab_Description"						"Greater Treant wields thick trunks, cleaving nearby enemy units with each attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_treant_large_tree_grab_cleave_damage_percent"				"%CLEAVE DAMAGE:"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_surge_lua"											"SURGE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_surge_lua_Description"								"Charges a target friendly unit with power, giving it a brief burst of phased movement speed. Allows the unit to reach maximum movement speed and cannot be slowed."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_surge_lua_shard_Description"						"Surge's duration is increased by %duration% seconds. For every 100 units of distance the target travels, the cooldown of a random on-cooldown ability is reduced by %cd_reduce% seconds. Abilities with less than %cd_min% seconds of cooldown remaining are unaffected."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_surge_lua_Lore"										"Ish'Kafel once used his speed of mind to navigate the maze between the walls."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_surge_lua_Note0"									"Units affected by Surge are immune to slows, unless the Surge effect expires."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_surge_lua_duration"									"DURATION:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_surge_lua_cd_reduce"									"COOLDOWN REDUCTION:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dark_seer_surge_lua_cd_min"									"MIN REMAINING COOLDOWN TO REDUCE:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dark_seer_surge_lua"							"Surge"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dark_seer_surge_lua_Description"				"Movement speed increased to %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_ABSOLUTE_MIN%."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_lua"								"MAGIC MISSILE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_lua_Description"					"Fires a Magic Missile at an enemy unit, stunning and dealing damage."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_lua_shard_description"			"Can bounce off enemies %bounce_count% times, with the bounce range equal to the Magic Missile's cast range. If an enemy is attacking or casting on the caster, Magic Missile deals an additional %bonus_damage_pct%%% damage and stuns the target."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_lua_Lore"						"Magic Missile is a humble martial technique of the Skywrath lineage, and now it serves as Syndel's primary instrument of vengeance."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_lua_magic_missile_stun"			"STUN DURATION:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_lua_magic_missile_damage"		"DAMAGE:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_lua_abilitycastrange"			"CAST RANGE:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_lua_bounce_count"			"BOUNCES:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_vengefulspirit_magic_missile_lua_bonus_damage_pct"			"%Damage of Being the Target:"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua"									"REAPER'S SCYTHE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_Description"						"Stuns the target, then deals damage based on how much life it is missing. If Necrophos kills an hero this way, he'll permanently gain Health and Mana Regen. If Reaper's Scythe kills the target, for every 1%% health the target remain, %cd_back%%% of Reaper's Scythe cooldown is reduced and %mana_back%%% of its mana cost is refunded."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_Lore"							"The amount of death and suffering in the air increases the power of Necrophos's plague magic."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_Note0"							"Damage is dealt at the end of the stun."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_damage_per_health"				"DAMAGE PER MISSING HP:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_stun_duration"					"STUN DURATION:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_hp_per_kill"						"HP REGEN:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_mana_per_kill"					"MANA REGEN:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_AbilityCastRange"					"CAST RANGE:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_stack"					"REAPER'S SCYTHE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_necrolyte_reapers_scythe_lua_stack_Description" "Permanently grant %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_HEALTH_REGEN_CONSTANT% Health Regeneration per second and %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MANA_REGEN_CONSTANT% Mana Regeneration per second on kills."

"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua"							"Luminosity"
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_Lore"						"Diminished in power without access to the Children's replenishing light, Valora can still recharge herself and her allies by creating order from the chaos which resides within each fight."
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_Description"				"After a number of attacks, Dawnbreaker powers up, charging her next attack with a critical hit that heals all allied heroes within %heal_radius% units around her for a portion of attack damage dealt. Creeps and neutral enemies provide less healing. Allies are healed for %allied_healing_pct%%% of the amount. <font color='#70EA72'>During the day, the critical strike damage and healing amount will increase by %bonus_damage_daytime%%%. </font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_Note0"						"Luminosity Heal is considered a lifesteal and increased by sources of Lifesteal Amplification."
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_bonus_damage"				"%CRITICAL STRIKE DAMAGE:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_heal_pct"					"%HEALING FROM HEROES:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_heal_from_creeps"			"%CREEP HEAL PENALTY:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_Ability_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_attack_count"				"ATTACKS REQUIRED:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua"							"Luminosity"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_dawnbreaker_luminosity_lua_Description"				"Powering up with Luminosity"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua"						"EMPOWERING HASTE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_Lore"					"Aspiring heroes gain speed and power from simply observing the Spirit Breaker's dominance on the battle field."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_Description"			"Spirit Breaker's attack damage increases based on his movement speed. Each kill on an enemy with his attacks grants permanent movement speed. Spirit Breaker can exceed the movement speed cap. Each level of EMPOWERING HASTE increases its stack count.<br><br>Base movement speed is not factored in.<br>If the hero's current movement speed is below his base movement speed, EMPOWERING HASTE provides no attack damage bonus."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_movespeed_damage_pct"	"%Movement Speed to Attack Damage Conversion Ratio: "
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_bonus_movespeed_per_kill"	"Movement Speed by Killing Heroes:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_bonus_movespeed_per_kill_creep"			"Movement Speed by Killing Creeps:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_basic_stack"			"Increase stacks each time you learn:"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua"							"EMPOWERING HASTE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_spirit_breaker_empowering_haste_lua_Description"				"Movement speed increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%"

