"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_faceless_void_time_lock_lua_stun_Description"		"You have been locked in time by Faceless Void!"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_skywrath_mage_shield_of_the_scion_lua"					"SKYWRATH'S AEGIS"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_skywrath_mage_shield_of_the_scion_lua_Description"		"Each time Skywrath Mage deals magic damage to an enemy with an ability, he gains a buff that grants bonus Intelligence and Armor. Each charge from a separate cast stacks independently. Skywrath's Aegis enters cooldown after %stack_to_cooldown% triggers."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_skywrath_mage_shield_of_the_scion_lua_stack_duration"			"Charge Duration: "
