"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_skywrath_mage_shield_of_the_scion_lua_buff_Description"	"Grants %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_STATS_INTELLECT_BONUS% bonus Intelligence and %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_PHYSICAL_ARMOR_BONUS% bonus Armor."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_rip_tide_lua"								"RIP TIDE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_rip_tide_lua_Description"					"Naga Siren and her allied units within %aura_radius% range strike all nearby enemy units with a damaging wave of water after every %hits% attacks. This wave reduces enemies' Armor for %duration% seconds."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_naga_siren_rip_tide_lua_Lore"							"Enemies of Naga Siren are swept by torrents surging from the deep ocean, their defenses shattered utterly."
