"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_neutral_upgrade_lua"										"Evolution"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_neutral_upgrade_lua_Description"							"This neutral creature will be enchanted after each round. \n Attack Speed increases by %attack_speed%\n Base Attack Interval Time decreases by %base_attack_time_reduction%, down to a minimum of %min_base_attack_time_reduction%\nArmor and magic resistance increased, and each round increased faster."
